OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSport concussion guidance  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto require 24-hour rest    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Anyone with suspected concussion must  
OL,6, be immediately removed from football,  
OL,7, rugby and other sports and rest for at 
OL,8, least 24 hours, under new guidance for 
OL,9, grassroots clubs.                      
OL,11,FIt says the NHS 111 help-line should be
OL,12,Fcalled and players should not return to
OL,13,Fcompetitive sport for at least 21 days.
OL,15,FThe UK-wide guidelines are aimed at    
OL,16,Fparents, coaches, referees and players.
OL,18,FIts authors say a "culture change" in  
OL,19,Fthe way head injuries are dealt with is
OL,20,Fneeded.                                
